description: After a good run of extreme sports in extreme weather, you probably require extreme deliciousness, and that's where Wook Waffaz Waffle Emporium comes in. They're whipping up a wonderfully tasty selection of whimsical waffle sandwich creations, like Buffalo Chicken, Sausage & Gravy, Pulled Pork, and more. If you're feelin' sweet, treat yourself to Blueberry, Cinnamon Sugar, S'more, etc...So come snowboard over here to this big green truck stat, and satisfy your adventurous appetite with an extremely energizing eggo-alternative, courtesy of Wook Waffaz Waffle Emporium.
name: Wook Waffaz Waffle Emporium
